                        <button class="faq-toggle flex justify-between items-center w-full text-left group" data-faq="3">
                            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-heading-1 group-hover:text-[#1E6DEB] dark:group-hover:text-[#EAF2FF] transition-colors duration-200">When will we start seeing results?</h3>
                            <svg class="faq-icon w-4 h-4 text-heading-3 transform transition-transform duration-300 ease-out" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-content hidden mt-3 text-sm text-heading-3 leading-relaxed overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="faq-content-inner">
                                <p>Results depend on your current presence and package level, but typical milestones are:</p>
                                <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                                    <li>Weeks 1-2: setup, planning, and baseline optimization</li>
                                    <li>Month 1: improved consistency and engagement activity</li>
                                    <li>Month 2-3: stronger reach, audience growth, and campaign performance</li>
                                    <li>Ongoing: continual optimization through insights and reporting</li>
                                </ul>
